<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'About' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- About Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Alma Brazil</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Travel can be deeper, more personal and more connected when it is guided by trust.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Story -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-story">
        <div class="about-story-text">
          <h2>My Story</h2>
          <p>I was born in Brazil and have spent over 15 years working between Brazil, the UK and the United States, supporting international productions across the country.</p>
          <p>That work took me across Brazil, from major cities to remote regions, managing logistics, teams and high-pressure environments.</p>
          <p>It taught me how to move through this country with awareness, structure and calm. And more importantly, how to make it work for others.</p>
          <p>Many women are drawn to Brazil, but hesitate. Because it can feel overwhelming, unpredictable or unsafe to navigate alone.</p>
          <p>Alma Brazil is how I make Brazil accessible, safe and meaningful for other women.</p>
          <p class="signature">— Raquel</p>

          <div class="credentials">
            <h3>Background</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>15+ years working across Brazil with international teams</li>
              <li>Production work for BBC, Netflix and Amazon</li>
              <li>Experience managing logistics, safety and complex environments</li>
              <li>Deep understanding of how to move through Brazil with confidence</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/Raquel.png" alt="Raquel - Your Guide" class="about-photo">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes This Different -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes This Different</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>I Am Not a Tour Operator</h3>
          <p>I am a producer. With over 15 years working across Brazil with international productions, I know how to navigate complexity, anticipate problems and make things flow. That experience becomes your safety, your access and your ease.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Every Journey Is Designed Around You</h3>
          <p>I don't follow scripts or fixed itineraries. I design each journey around you, combining local insight, trusted networks, thoughtful planning and space for things to unfold naturally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>I Am There to Hold the Experience</h3>
          <p>I am there not just to organise, but to hold the experience so you can relax into it. I don't take you through the country. I walk alongside you as it unfolds.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Every journey begins with a conversation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-it-works">
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="how-step-number">1</div>
          <h3>We Talk</h3>
          <p>I take the time to understand how you travel, what you're looking for, and what might feel uncertain to you. This is not just about preferences. It's about designing something that actually works for you in Brazil.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="how-step-number">2</div>
          <h3>I Design</h3>
          <p>I build your journey based on real conditions on the ground. Where to stay. How to move. What's worth your time, and what isn't. Everything is considered so the experience flows without friction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <div class="how-step-number">3</div>
          <h3>You Experience</h3>
          <p>Once you arrive, you're not figuring things out alone. I support you throughout, so you can move with confidence, relax into the experience, and focus on being present. You are held, but never restricted.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Women -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Women</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <p>Brazil can be an incredible place to experience, but it can also feel uncertain to navigate alone.</p>
          <p>That changes everything about how you move, what you choose to do, and how much you're able to relax into the experience.</p>
          <p>This is why I work with women. Not to create something exclusive, but to create something more considered.</p>
          <p>Travelling with the right support changes how you experience the country. You feel safer. You move with more confidence. You are more open to what's around you.</p>
          <p>And that creates a different kind of trip. Not just where you go, but how you experience it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Ready to Begin?</h2>
        <p>Explore the journeys or get in touch to start shaping your experience.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/journeys" class="btn btn-primary">The Journeys</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
